{"tid":1412101,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[緊急][討論][置頂]連登係咪慢慢走緊向獨裁之路？？？","createTime":"2019-08-05T05:26:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T06:31:34.000Z","uid":76543,"like":122,"dislike":37,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"a672d01be84af1c6450f0d0cd9f5b886ff8bedcb","tid":1412101,"uid":76543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T05:26:01.000Z","msg":"首先我哋係為香港人爭取一個民主自由嘅社會 <br />\n但係人哋返工嘅意願同自由我哋又唔比 <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>咁咩係自由</strong></span></span><br />\n自由唔係應該尊重各方意見咩？<br />\n<br />\n好似前線行動慢慢升級 我哋和理非都唔同你哋割蓆<br />\n因為我哋覺得點都好 我哋係同路人<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>不割蓆 不分化 不篤灰</strong></span></span><br />\n但係我哋俾少少意見前線 你哋就一句前線有決定 你唔喺前線就唔好嘈咁<br />\n會唔會你哋覺得我唔割 就開始借勢屌一啲持少少相反意見嘅人呢<br />\n民主自由係你哋都要學習接受我哋和理非嘅意見 去一齊討論<br />\n<br />\n好似今日咁 我好支持地鐵不合作活動 但係有唔少人問點解要做到封路呢？<br />\n封路令到好多消防同救護車嚟唔到 你哋話你哋會讓路 問題係架車塞咗喺中間<br />\n<br />\n就算係要做香港獨立 你都係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>要一個民主同自由嘅香港</strong></span></span> 但係少少反對意見都接受唔到 咁最後只會係另外一個獨裁國家<br />\n<br />\n不如兩邊意見都試下唔好互屌<br />\n一齊討論 唔係淨係鬧<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>光復香港<br />\n時代革命</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"fbf7055c9c50d1602ba7b9f934a564a4b9be6c50","tid":1412101,"uid":76543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T05:26:17.000Z","msg":"自推十次"},{"pid":"e23aef6bfa64bff783b2ca332ed7244940d94dbc","tid":1412101,"uid":76543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T05:26:29.000Z","msg":"一齊討論"},{"pid":"a4db24636cfb022536241926eaf20e7579dee409","tid":1412101,"uid":76543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T05:26:42.000Z","msg":"光復香港"},{"pid":"2b4e95eed3f9cebb5accbe5bf453fdb7a3212b79","tid":1412101,"uid":76543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T05:26:54.000Z","msg":"時代革命"},{"pid":"e59fac9814baccb71678da1b25ff73447bc19e43","tid":1412101,"uid":76543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T05:27:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4a279c60b00c225836ac88e2aac3dc651ade63c","tid":1412101,"uid":76543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T05:27:16.000Z","msg":"五大訴求"},{"pid":"be21a23b7c45255f65a4c4caa900362de598ab49","tid":1412101,"uid":89184,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T05:27:21.000Z","msg":"其實我哋嘅方向應該  係我哋本身爭取緊基本法賦予我哋人權、香港自治、真雙普選嘅權利<br />\n<br />\n呢啲權利本身合情合理<br />\n<br />\n但係共產黨依家破壞咗一個兩制， 破壞咗基本法<br />\n<br />\n所以我地<span style=\"color: red;\">先至</span>唔再相信一國兩制同基本法<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以，<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">重點係，中共破壞中英聯合聲明、基本法、一國兩制在先!!!</span></span><br />\n<br />\n中英聯合聲明失效，即係<span style=\"color: red;\">香港主權懸空</span>，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">要求國際社會（尤其美國同英國）同香港人一齊重新討論和解決香港的主權問題</span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong><br />\n香港自治!<br />\n五大訴求!<br />\n真雙普選!</strong></span>"},{"pid":"42f5e0891171950254d68d73f2c38bf043ecd8ae","tid":1412101,"uid":76543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T05:27:26.000Z","msg":"缺一不可"},{"pid":"79cfe675bad96945ee8a5d3d469adc2d75be6732","tid":1412101,"uid":76543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T05:28:29.000Z","msg":"光復香港"},{"pid":"28d9b5f8f90646ca17f6cfddf744cfad27a4f92d","tid":1412101,"uid":76543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T05:28:40.000Z","msg":"時代革命"},{"pid":"654efce83d55b2ae1929837c3af50c3ebbf6b209","tid":1412101,"uid":76543,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy"